<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>회원가입</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/join.css">
  <script src="../js/join.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-3 formsizing company-register">
    <h1>회원가입</h1>

    <form action="/action_page.php" id="join">
      <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
        <label>아이디</label> <br>
        <label class="la2" for="email">*&nbsp;사용자 ID는 5~20자의 영문 소문자, 숫자와 특수기호(_),(-)만 사용 가능하며 영문으로 시작되어야 합니다.</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="id" placeholder="ex) malfoy123" name="id">
        <span class="error_next_box green" id="idMsg-green" style="display:none" aria-live="assertive">멋진 아이디네요!</span>
        <span class="error_next_box" id="idMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">5~20자의 영문 소문자, 숫자와 특수기호(_),(-)만 사용 가능합니다.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
        <label>비밀번호</label> <br>
        <label class="la2" for="pass">*&nbsp;비밀번호는 8~16자로 영문 대 소문자, 숫자, 특수문자로 이루어져야 합니다.</label>
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pass" placeholder="ex) password123 " name="pass">
        <span class="error_next_box" id="pswd1Msg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">8~16자 영문 대 소문자, 숫자, 특수문자를 사용하세요.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3 mt-3">
        <label>비밀번호 재확인</label> <br>
        <!-- <label class="la2" for="pass">*&nbsp;비밀번호를 재확인합니다.</label> -->
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pass" name="pass">
        <span class="error_next_box" id="pswd2Msg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>이름</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요." name="name">
        <span class="error_next_box" id="nameMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">한글과 영문 대 소문자를 사용하세요. (특수기호, 공백 사용 불가)</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>전화번호</label>
        <input type="url" class="form-control" id="tel" placeholder="ex) 010-1111-2222" name="tel">
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>이메일 주소</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="ex) box@gmail.com" name="email">
        <span class="error_next_box" id="emailMsg" style="display:none;" aria-live="assertive">이메일 주소를 다시 확인해주세요.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>생년월일</label>
        <input type="date" class="form-control" id="bir" name="bir">
      </div>
      
      <div class="mb-3 zip">
        <label>우편번호</label>
        <div class="zipInput">
          <input type="text" class="form-control zip" id="zip" name="zip" disabled>
          <input type="button" value="우편번호 검색">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>주소1</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="add1" name="add1" disabled>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-3">
        <label>주소2</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="add2" placeholder="ex) box@gmail.com" name="add2">
      </div>

      <div class="btn-center-box">
        <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg  mx-2">회원가입</button></a>
        <a href="#"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg  mx-2">취소</button></a>
      </div>

    </form>

  </div>
</body>

</html>